'''Tinɣir''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵜⵉⵏⵖⵉⵔ''') d [[tamdint]] id yezgan deg tama n usamar n [[Merruk|Tgelda tameṛṛukit]] deg uzaɣar n Tudɣa ar tuffɣa n [[aṭlas ameqran|Weṭlas Afellay]] af udem n [[Adrar n Seɣṛu|Wedrar n Saɣru]]. D tamaneɣt n [[Tasga n Tiɣir]] seg useggwas n 2009. Deg 2004 akk iɣerman d wemdan n tɣiwant-agi ɣur-sen azal n  86.500 imezdaɣen tuget-nsen d [[imaziɣen]]

=Tinɣir d Tmaziɣt=

Akk imezdaɣen llan d [[imaziɣen]], ttmeslayen akk gar-asen s [[Tamaziɣt n weṭlas alemmas]] maca qqaren tutlayt nnsen tacelḥit. Deg temnaṭ, llant ttzdiɣent [[Tawsit|tiwsitin]] timaziɣin am [[Ayt Ɛeṭṭa]] ar tama n wenẓul, [[Ayt Merɣad]] deg wegmuḍ, [[Ayt Ḥdidu]] deg ugafa et [[Ayt Yafelman|Ayt Yafelman.]]

